# ORIG TITLE    North Korea orders rocket batteries to target US Pacific bases . 
# ORIG CONTENT  North Korea has ordered its rocket batteries to be on standby to attack US bases in South Korea and the Pacific. According to state media North Korean leader Kim Jong-un chaired an emergency meeting of top generals and “judged the time has come to settle accounts with the US imperialists in view of the prevailing situation.” . The tension has cranked up notch after the US flew Stealth bombers over South Korea in a show of strength to Pyongyang. 
